Reasoning: The paper focuses on investigating the features that make natural scenes memorable, which involves analyzing and predicting visual features. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a deep neural network-based predictor, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The use of a large-scale database and the analysis of handcrafted features suggest that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the use of a deep neural network suggests that the paper may also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
